org.locationtech.geowave.core.store.ingest

Interface LocalFileIngestPlugin<O>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - The type of data to write to GeoWave
    All Superinterfaces:
    DataAdapterProvider<O>, IndexProvider, IngestPluginBase<URL,O>, LocalPluginBase
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractLocalIngestWithMapper, AbstractSimpleFeatureIngestPlugin, GDELTIngestPlugin, GeoLifeIngestPlugin, GeoToolsRasterDataStoreIngestPlugin, GeoToolsVectorDataStoreIngestPlugin, GeoWaveAvroIngestPlugin, GpxIngestPlugin, Stanag4676IngestPlugin, TdriveIngestPlugin, TwitterIngestPlugin

    public interface LocalFileIngestPlugin<O>
extends LocalPluginBase, IngestPluginBase<URL,O>, IndexProvider
    This is the primary plugin for directly ingesting data to GeoWave from local files. It will write any GeoWaveData that is emitted for any supported file.
